  "title": "🌟 Events Marketing (Travel Opportunities)",
  "description": "<p><strong>🚀 Ready to Kickstart Your Career? Join a Team That Grows With You!</strong></p>\n<p>We’re looking for driven, outgoing, and ambitious individuals (just like you!) to join our sales and marketing team. Whether you're fresh out of school, uni, or looking to level up your first job, this is your chance to build real skills, grow fast, and be part of something exciting.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🔍 What We’re Looking For:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A positive, go-getter mindset—you love learning and pushing yourself</li>\n  <li>Natural leadership energy (even if you’re still developing it!)</li>\n  <li>A team player who enjoys connecting with people and making an impact</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>💼 What You’ll Be Doing:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Learning the ins and outs of ethical sales—done with purpose and integrity</li>\n  <li>Leading and motivating your peers toward shared goals</li>\n  <li>Building real relationships with clients, customers, and teammates</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>🔥 Why You'll Love Working With Us:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>1-on-1 mentorship to guide your growth every step of the way</li>\n  <li>Real career progression—based on performance, not time served</li>\n  <li>Fun, supportive, and family-like team culture</li>\n  <li>Travel opportunities (local and international!)</li>\n  <li>A fast-moving environment where your work actually makes a difference</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>🎯 This role is perfect if you’re:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A recent graduate, early in your career, or ready to switch things up</li>\n  <li>Looking to gain real-world experience and leadership skills</li>\n  <li>Eager to be part of a business that invests in <em>you</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>📩 Sound like your kind of adventure?</strong></p>\n<p>Hit <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> and send us your resume—we can’t wait to meet you!</p>\n<p>(Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.)</p>",
